com.company.demo.transaction

Class Transaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.company.demo.transaction.Transaction

  • public class Transaction
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for creating transaction object to store information about a transaction. This is a model class, there is nothing more than fields and getter methods. Since a transaction is a one time process and it can't be modified, the fields in the transaction except status are final.
